  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class StatisticCollection
extends CollectionNode<StatisticCollection>
    This StatisticCollection is the root of the PubSub-tree. It does have several concrete DataNode children where new data may be set (you may use this StatisticCollection to subscribe to a CollectionNode to get all data which is published within this subtree)
